{"tid":1273836,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"更有效讓人了解政治的網站","createTime":"2019-07-01T14:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:25:42.000Z","uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6800854f0bf892f53fa7bf38803a1d425e4ab2f1","tid":1273836,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"討論造一個幫助投票嘅軟件<br />\n<br />\n覺得政治人物資料太多， 很難全面地了解再去投票嗎？<br />\n<br />\n相信各投票的國家都面對這些情況。<br />\n<br />\n其實網上關於政治人物嘅新聞係要分類出來嘅，<br />\n我們需要一個網站， list 哂所有政治人物資料， 用一句總結佢地做過嘅每件突別事或說過的話， 同埋詳細資料。<br />\n<br />\n申請account 需要某d每個人獨有嘅資料辦別， 等佢地唔駛重覆，並且有一個類似reddit 嘅投票機制， 去初步知道票數。<br />\n<br />\n等人投票前可以參考自已侯選人嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔太熟香港嘅投票環境， 但我估而家嘅香港政客係代表某一小眾人嘅利益而上位嘅。"},{"pid":"faed7edf1fce32e8157bca7c78cf609d81204142","tid":1273836,"uid":55597,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"詐訓既人係唔會醒"},{"pid":"6b083e66cfe567691f5ff15caec3a674a7af3f94","tid":1273836,"uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"200萬人攞棍9沖贏唔到共產黨架。"},{"pid":"05173c228591e7162c620cce562804bbe8641225","tid":1273836,"uid":25166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"照咁睇<br />\n寫唔難 content先最難"},{"pid":"115ded19e98ce1ff796fcd7af30691ed6b712082","tid":1273836,"uid":25166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05173c228591e7162c620cce562804bbe8641225","tid":1273836,"uid":25166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"照咁睇<br />\n寫唔難 content先最難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"下半部分唔明你講咩"},{"pid":"84b9c9dc13e83fa2968cdbe2bfe99cf850e89a0b","tid":1273836,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05173c228591e7162c620cce562804bbe8641225","tid":1273836,"uid":25166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"照咁睇<br />\n寫唔難 content先最難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15: